                    "tone": "neutral"
                }
            ],
            "said": false
        },
        {
            "lines": [
                {
                    "text": "So far, I'm happy with how this is coming along so far. It did take 12+ hours to get it to this stage however... Anyways, I'll get back to you after you solve the next puzzle! Good luck!",
